We weren't used to it.

122
00:06:19,520 --> 00:06:22,050
- And it uses a lot of electricity.
- I could've just driven over to get it.

123
00:06:22,088 --> 00:06:22,720
No need to come.

124
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:25,080
Do you know
how much gas costs these days?

125
00:06:25,080 --> 00:06:25,909
Labor power.

126
00:06:25,910 --> 00:06:27,240
