184
00:08:37,550 --> 00:08:39,400
Laugh it up. What's so funny?

185
00:08:40,355 --> 00:08:41,280
You've got the money.

186
00:08:41,800 --> 00:08:42,710
Do something useful.

187
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:44,160
Go check

188
00:08:44,160 --> 00:08:46,190
if the vacuum's full of dust

189
00:08:46,190 --> 00:08:46,830
and empty it.

190
00:08:47,040 --> 00:08:47,480
On it.

191
00:08:49,044 --> 00:08:49,830
You're right.

192
00:08:49,830 --> 00:08:50,640
All this dirt.

193
00:08:52,520 --> 00:08:53,640
I'll take care of this.

194
00:08:55,377 --> 00:08:56,760
Be right back to take care of that!

195
00:08:56,800 --> 00:08:57,933
I'll come back and tidy that!

196
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:58,360
You...

197
00:08:58,520 --> 00:09:00,000
Mom, see? You let go a little

198
00:09:00,190 --> 00:09:01,710
