199
00:09:02,310 --> 00:09:04,280
Being the one
who manages everything is hard work.

200
00:09:04,280 --> 00:09:06,430
Look at this. Can I not step in?

201
00:09:06,430 --> 00:09:07,422
There's a mess everywhere.

202
00:09:07,466 --> 00:09:07,790
Yes.

203
00:09:08,710 --> 00:09:09,400
Look at this!

204
00:09:10,790 --> 00:09:12,240
Leave it there. I'll take care of it.

205
00:09:12,240 --> 00:09:13,070
