207
00:09:14,688 --> 00:09:15,950
- Stop. I'll do it.
- Seriously.

208
00:09:16,355 --> 00:09:17,400
You're going to handle it?

209
00:09:17,400 --> 00:09:18,750
I don't want to control everything.

210
00:09:18,755 --> 00:09:20,160
