stop letting your imagination run wild.

312
00:14:14,880 --> 00:14:15,240
I...

313
00:14:15,520 --> 00:14:17,480
We shouldn't criticize Shen Dai.

314
00:14:17,910 --> 00:14:20,160
Shen Dai is imaginative,
and she's a bit of a loner.

315
00:14:20,480 --> 00:14:22,070
