316
00:14:23,240 --> 00:14:24,520
Grandpa, you're so biased.

317
00:14:24,590 --> 00:14:25,360
It's not biased.

318
00:14:25,640 --> 00:14:27,310
Her personality is why she's able

319
00:14:27,670 --> 00:14:29,280
to do artistic work now? Right?

320
00:14:29,400 --> 00:14:30,590
Dad, you've got taste.

321
00:14:30,760 --> 00:14:32,000
You're so good to me.

322
00:14:32,360 --> 00:14:33,360
I'm touched.

323
00:14:33,610 --> 00:14:34,400
