with Headmaster Zhang.

351
00:15:59,790 --> 00:16:01,350
In the end, he gave in and signed

352
00:16:01,480 --> 00:16:02,550
the situation report.

353
00:16:02,844 --> 00:16:04,149
I took it to the finance office

354
