373
00:16:36,830 --> 00:16:37,440
Bai.

374
00:16:37,920 --> 00:16:39,040
Here's to you. Thank you.

375
00:16:39,133 --> 00:16:39,830
Don't mention it.

376
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:42,310
Right.

377
00:16:43,960 --> 00:16:45,830
When I was negotiating
the overdue payment,

378
00:16:45,866 --> 00:16:47,650
I also brought up
the school uniform order.

379
00:16:48,688 --> 00:16:50,280
