the school uniform contract too.

386
00:17:04,630 --> 00:17:05,440
Really?

387
00:17:06,440 --> 00:17:07,790
3,000 pieces!

388
00:17:07,870 --> 00:17:09,000
That's a huge order!

389
00:17:09,760 --> 00:17:10,310
That said,

390
00:17:10,577 --> 00:17:12,870
