394
00:17:19,150 --> 00:17:20,720
and still end up not making a profit.

395
00:17:22,550 --> 00:17:22,960
It's okay.

396
00:17:23,590 --> 00:17:24,920
Uniforms are all about volume.

397
00:17:27,040 --> 00:17:30,310
If I can land this deal,

398
00:17:31,550 --> 00:17:33,350
the company will scale up.

399
00:17:33,760 --> 00:17:35,520
No more a family workshop.

400
00:17:35,920 --> 00:17:37,390
You've got the long-term vision.

401
00:17:37,830 --> 00:17:39,870
Should we go see
Headmaster Zhang together?

402
00:17:40,150 --> 00:17:41,480
Sure. Let's go tomorrow.

403
00:17:41,600 --> 00:17:42,200
Sounds good.

404
00:17:42,870 --> 00:17:43,520
Bai,

405
00:17:43,520 --> 00:17:46,000
you really are my lucky star
on the road to success.

406
00:17:46,550 --> 00:17:47,280
You're too kind.

407
00:17:48,280 --> 00:17:48,960
Thank you.

408
00:17:54,440 --> 00:17:55,440
That's

409
00:17:55,466 --> 00:17:56,200
the situation.

