430
00:18:36,280 --> 00:18:37,920
But after working with you,

431
00:18:38,240 --> 00:18:39,590
I feel like you are

432
00:18:39,830 --> 00:18:41,280
more meticulous, and more thoughtful.

433
00:18:42,070 --> 00:18:42,550
Also,

434
00:18:42,550 --> 00:18:43,590
this price point was set

435
00:18:43,830 --> 00:18:44,870
after careful research.

436
00:18:44,911 --> 00:18:46,444
