another opportunity instead.

439
00:18:55,110 --> 00:18:55,760
Let's go, Lina.

440
00:18:59,711 --> 00:19:00,488
Headmaster Zhang.

441
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:01,550
I'll do it.

442
00:19:04,350 --> 00:19:05,200
Starting a business

443
00:19:05,280 --> 00:19:07,590
