444
00:19:08,070 --> 00:19:08,480
right?

445
00:19:11,520 --> 00:19:12,150
Then,

446
00:19:12,680 --> 00:19:13,790
I thank you, Ms. Liu.

447
00:19:15,440 --> 00:19:16,150
You're welcome.

448
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:22,310
Here's some info on Le Shuishan.

449
00:19:22,720 --> 00:19:23,960
She's from Suzhou.

450
00:19:24,150 --> 00:19:25,040
She's retired now,

451
00:19:25,110 --> 00:19:26,329
