452
00:19:26,330 --> 00:19:28,109
She has a good reputation
and high EQ,

453
00:19:28,110 --> 00:19:30,380
(Le Shuishan, Makeup Artist)
so she's invited to work events

454
00:19:30,380 --> 00:19:31,600
