504
00:22:49,133 --> 00:22:50,777
Tastes just like I remembered!

505
00:22:53,870 --> 00:22:54,630
Eat up, Qing!

506
00:22:55,440 --> 00:22:56,590
I'm not that hungry.

507
00:23:02,755 --> 00:23:03,580
