You have to keep warm!"

522
00:23:49,520 --> 00:23:50,480
It drove me crazy.

523
00:23:55,000 --> 00:23:56,200
Thinking back,

524
00:23:58,110 --> 00:23:59,070
she was probably

525
00:23:59,550 --> 00:24:00,920
