548
00:25:12,520 --> 00:25:13,720
In her final days,

549
00:25:15,222 --> 00:25:16,480
lying in that hospital bed...

550
00:25:21,040 --> 00:25:21,550
I...

551
00:25:23,440 --> 00:25:24,440
I told her,

552
00:25:25,200 --> 00:25:25,760
"Mom...

553
00:25:30,790 --> 00:25:31,350
I'm sorry.

554
00:25:34,070 --> 00:25:35,870
We probably won't get to Xinjiang."

555
00:25:40,590 --> 00:25:41,480
She couldn't

556
00:25:42,150 --> 00:25:43,630
